<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038552" n="169r"/>
<p>Accepi quas mihi transmisisti <rs type="letter">litteras</rs>, pro quibus gratias ago maxi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mas; ecce hic <rs type="letter">responsionem</rs> meam ad <rs type="letter">litteras</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1156417392">Alberti Friderici
        <lb/>Gutt</rs>, quam rogo ut <date when="1719-01-21">die Sabbathi</date> sub involucro ad <rs type="person">Patrem 
            <lb/>O<choice><orig>^</orig><reg>'</reg></choice>Kelly</rs> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3169070">Romam</rs> mittas. Excusa qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so molestiam, pro
    <lb/>hoc favore Tibi coram gratias agam, spero enim me
    <lb/>ad Te venturum <date when="1719-01-22">die Dominica</date> vel <date when="1719-01-23">die Lun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></date>. <abbr>Ill.mus</abbr><del><gap/></del> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lenus</rs> Te salutat gratias agens pro oblatione Tua amica
    <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_MJFBHDTR">Optic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118634771">Wolfii</rs>; ea opus non habet, quia ipse <add>nunc</add> possidet
    <lb/><del>nunc </del>totum Opus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118634771">Wolfianum</rs>.</p> <closer><salute>Vale.</salute> <dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728"><abbr>Pat.</abbr></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1719-01-19">19. <abbr>Jan.</abbr> 1719</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
</body>
